The Citizens Holding Company - Mission & Goals








Citizens Holding Company


Mission & Goals
 The Citizens Bank’s Vision Statement	The first choice for consumers, business, industry and government.	  The Citizens Bank’s Mission Statement	Improving your quality of life and economic well-being.	  The Citizens Bank’s Values Statement	Serving with integrity, dedication, competence, hospitality and The Golden Rule.



