The Citizens Holding Company - Banking - Philadelphia, MS








Citizens Holding Company


Welcome
 Citizens Holding Company is the parent company of The Citizens Bank of Philadelphia.  Headquartered in Philadelphia, Mississippi  Twenty-three banking locations in Mississippi  Full-service commercial banking  Mortgage loans & title insurance services  Offering a full range of Internet banking services Citizens Holding Company's stock is listed on the NASDAQ Stock Exchange as CIZN.	  Mississippi Business Journal names Leaders in Finance. The Citizens Bank's Travis Moore was named a Leader in Finance by the Mississippi Business Journal.   	  The Citizens Bank receives the Community Connect Award at the Q2 Client Conference in Austin, Texas. The award was given to clients that exhibited unique and creative ways to give back to their communities.	 



